{"tid":1197340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"記得盡量令到警方搜證困難，如果想衝","createTime":"2019-06-10T03:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T03:26:39.000Z","uid":51714,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"04c952b5ad60787a62047bd8e7cbaa6a65cc4260","tid":1197340,"uid":51714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"衝定唔衝，各自修為，自己諗。<br />\n但香港法律係要舉證責任在控方，同埋唔好比人搵到證明你有強烈犯罪動機，所以第一次參加運動素人要留意<br />\n<strong>1)請記得戴眼罩、口罩，避免被任何鏡頭影到</strong><br />\n(呢點唔洗點解釋，比人影到在場好難講得通)<br />\n<strong>2)請著低調素色衫，或者著一次就可以掉果d</strong><br />\n(唔好比人上你屋企搜到證物，亦唔好咁易辨認)<br />\n<strong>3)請搭地鐵買飛巴士入錢，唔好用個人八達通</strong><br />\n(慈母可以掌握到你出入閘時間架)<br />\n<strong>4)千奇唔好唔好打卡自拍post ig/fb/share比朋友，你唔係去嘉年華</strong><br />\n(你重要post比人睇就真係無得救)<br />\n<strong>5)若要通知朋友家人位置，請善用tg 已讀delete功能</strong><br />\n(唔好係電話保留任何證據，雖然慈母一定有方法搵到，但記得要增加佢困難)"},{"pid":"2d240a90a4c9f05ab2771cef32c05437bec9f0d7","tid":1197340,"uid":52230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T03:13:23.000Z","msg":"黎回帶喇喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tpMi7BS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtpMi7BS.gif&h=51ec2d0c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aq35NBW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAq35NBW.gif&h=92c663f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J4YmkWY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4YmkWY.gif&h=27ed1f34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yd7qNBZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyd7qNBZ.gif&h=5df36879&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6XEs0W1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6XEs0W1.gif&h=c456d7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CVnqNB4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t